reviews.name: Organic Baby Food - Pears Apples & Baby Rice Ella's Kitchen 6 x 3.5 oz Box
reviews.reviewText: This is a great portable meal for the under-6-month babies. I would love to see more of the baby rice pouches!
reviews.title: Love this mix!

reviews.name: Organic Baby Food - Pears Apples & Baby Rice Ella's Kitchen 6 x 3.5 oz Box
reviews.reviewText: My 10 month old loves this baby rice. I started feeding this to him when he was 6 months old and he still loves it, smooth rice puree with delicious pear and apple. I serve it cold, straight out of the pouch.
reviews.title: Delicous Baby Rice

reviews.name: Organic Baby Food - Pears Apples & Baby Rice Ella's Kitchen 6 x 3.5 oz Box
reviews.reviewText: I even enjoyed this flavor. My baby really enjoyed the texture. Sometimes that is not always the case.
reviews.title: great flavors!

reviews.name: Organic Baby Food - Pears Apples & Baby Rice Ella's Kitchen 6 x 3.5 oz Box
reviews.reviewText: My son loves all of the Ella's Kitchen flavors mixed with the baby rice! He tends to like his food a bit thicker and this is perfect!
reviews.title: One of My Son's Favorites

reviews.name: Organic Baby Food - Pears Apples & Baby Rice Ella's Kitchen 6 x 3.5 oz Box
reviews.reviewText: Bought this along with other Ella's Kitchen foods and my baby girl LOVES it! Ella's Kitchen provides great quality baby food at a reasonable price.
reviews.title: Baby Love It!
